<main class="page"><p class="eyebrow">EFF NATIONALS • SECURE STAFF VIEW</p><h1>Leadership<br>Command Center.</h1><p class="lead narrow">See learner progress, identify who needs encouragement, and review leadership assignments across the movement.</p><div id="staffGate" class="notice">Checking secure staff access…</div><div id="staffDashboard" hidden><div class="dashboard"><article class="stat"><b id="learnerCount">—</b><span>registered learners</span></article><article class="stat"><b id="completionCount">—</b><span>lesson completions</span></article><article class="stat"><b id="submissionCount">—</b><span>submitted assignments</span></article></div><section class="table-wrap"><div class="table-title"><h2>Learner progress</h2><input id="staffSearch" type="search" placeholder="Search name, email, chapter, role"></div><div class="table-scroll"><table><thead><tr><th>Learner</th><th>Chapter / role</th><th>Lessons completed</th><th>Last activity</th></tr></thead><tbody id="staffRows"></tbody></table></div></section><section class="table-wrap"><div class="table-title"><h2>Leadership assignments</h2><span class="small-note">Newest submissions first</span></div><div class="table-scroll"><table><thead><tr><th>Learner</th><th>Lesson</th><th>Response</th><th>Submitted</th></tr></thead><tbody id="submissionRows"></tbody></table></div></section></div></main>
